RankBaseMixtureSpectrumScorer - Class in org.Spectrums
Rank base scorer for mixture spectrum, due to the rank-base probability model is base on single peptide, ranks in mixture spectrum might not be corrected, need to adjust the peak rank base on the two peptides being considered
